4. regression testing -------yes we are doing but for unit testing we are doing it manually for all other tests we have automated it using jenkins.

In the above context, regression means a situation where a change in the code causes a previously working functionality to fail or behave incorrectly.
 Regression testing is a technique to prevent or detect such regressions by re-running existing tests after code changes. Â¹Â²

